iting (film)|Just Visiting]]'' \n|Hollywood Pictures||[[Hollywood Pictures]] and [[Gaumont Film Company|Gaumont]]; US distribution\n|-\n| align=\"right\"| May 25, 2001 || ''[[Pearl Harbor (film)|Pearl Harbor]]'' \n|Touchstone Pictures\n|[[Touchstone Pictures]] and Jerry Bruckheimer Films\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | June 15, 2001 || ''[[Atlantis: The Lost Empire]]'' \n|Walt Disney Pictures\n|[[Walt Disney Pictures]] and [[Walt Disney Feature Animation]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | June 29, 2001 || ''[[Crazy/Beautiful]]'' \n|Touchstone Pictures\n|[[Touchstone Pictures]] and Ulfland Productions\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | August 3, 2001 || ''[[The Princess Diaries (film)|The Princess Diaries]]'' \n|Walt Disney Pictures\n|[[Walt Disney Pictures]] and [[Whitney Houston|BrownHouse Productions]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | August 24, 2001 || ''[[Bubble Boy (film)|Bubble Boy]]'' \n| rowspan=\"2\" |Touchstone Pictures\n| \n|-\n| align=\"right\" | September 7, 2001 || ''[[New Port South]]'' ||[[John Hughes (filmmaker)|Hughes Entertainment]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | October 5, 2001 || ''[[Max Keeble's Big Move]]'' \n|Walt Disney Pictures\n|[[Walt Disney Pictures]] and Karz Entertainment\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | October 12, 2001 || ''[[Corky Romano]]'' \n| rowspan=\"2\" |Touchstone Pictures\n| \n|-\n| align=\"right\" | October 26, 2001 || ''[[High Heels and Low Lifes]]'' || Fragile Films\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | November 2, 2001 || ''[[Monsters, Inc.]]'' \n|Walt Disney Pictures\n|[[Walt Disney Pictures]] and [[Pixar|Pixar Animation Studios]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | November 21, 2001 || ''[[Out Cold (2001 film)|Out Cold]]'' \n| rowspan=\"2\" |Touchstone Pictures||[[Touchstone Pictures]], [[Spyglass Entertainment]] and <br /> [[The Donners' Company]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | December 14, 2001 || ''[[The Royal Tenenbaums]]''  ||  [[Touchstone Pictures]] and [[Wes Anderson|American Empirical Pictures]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | January 18, 2002 || ''[[Snow Dogs]]'' \n|Walt Disney Pictures\n|[[