le Lim Developing Animated Feature for Disney|url=https://www.awn.com/news/osnat-shurer-and-adele-lim-developing-animated-feature-disney|accessdate=October 10, 2018|work=Animation World Network|date=October 9, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first1=Petrana |last1=Radulovic |accessdate=August 24, 2019 |title=Disney announces Raya and the Last Dragon as next animated film|url=https://www.polygon.com/2019/8/24/20812723/raya-and-the-last-dragon-disney-animated-movie-release-date|newspaper=Polygon |date=August 24, 2019}}</ref>\n|Walt Disney Pictures\n|[[Walt Disney Animation Studios]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" |{{dts|2020|12|11|}}<ref name=\":0\" />||''[[Free Guy]]''\n| rowspan=\"3\" |20th Century Studios\n|Maximum Effort, [[21 Laps Entertainment]], Berlanti Productions, [[TSG Entertainment]], and Lit Entertainment Group\n|-\n| align=\"right\" |{{dts|2020|12|18|}}<ref name=\":0\" />||''[[West Side Story (2020 film)|West Side Story]]''\n|[[Amblin Entertainment]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" |{{dts|2020|12|25|}}<ref name=\":0\" />||''[[The Last Duel (2020 film)|The Last Duel]]''||[[Scott Free Productions]]\n|-\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | {{dts|2021|02|12|}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/box-office/disney-mulan-black-widow-release-dates-coronavirus-1203550173/|title=\u2018Black Widow,\u2019 \u2018Eternals,\u2019 \u2018Indiana Jones 5\u2019 and More Disney Films Get New Release Dates|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=April 3, 2020|accessdate=April 3, 2020}}</ref> || ''[[The Eternals (film)|The Eternals]]''\n|Marvel Studios|| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | February 26, 2021 ||''[[Ron's Gone Wrong]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |20th Century Studios\n| [[Locksmith Animation]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/amp/news/fox-locksmith-animation-unveil-rons-gone-wrong-1048037|title= Fox, Locksmith Animation Unveil 'Ron's Gone Wrong'|website=The Hollywood Reporter|last1=Ritman|first1=Alex|date=October 12, 2017|accessdate=February 17, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 