ilton' Movie With Original Broadway Cast Coming to Theaters|last1=Rubin|first1=Rebecca|date=February 3, 2020|work=Variety|accessdate=3 February 2020}}</ref>||''[[Hamilton (2021 film)|Hamilton]]''\n|[[Lin-Manuel Miranda|5000 Broadway Productions]] and [[RadicalMedia]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | {{dts|2021|11|05|}}<ref name=\":0\" />||''[[Marvel Cinematic Universe: Phase Four#Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness (2021)|Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness]]''\n|Marvel Studios\n|\n|-\n|{{dts|2021|12|17|}}<ref name=\"DisneyFox Release Date\" />\n|''[[Avatar 2]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |20th Century Studios\n|[[Lightstorm Entertainment]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" | {{dts|2022|01|14}}<ref name=\"DisneyFox Release Date\" />||''[[Nimona#Adaptations|Nimona]]''||[[Blue Sky Studios]] and [[Vertigo Entertainment]]\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | {{start date|2022|02|28|}}<ref name=\":0\" />||''[[Marvel Cinematic Universe: Phase Four#Thor: Love and Thunder (2021)|Thor: Love and Thunder]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Marvel Studios||\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | {{start date|2022|05|06|}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/black-panther-2-release-date-kit-haringtons-role-eternals-confirmed-1233149|title=Marvel Confirms Kit Harington for 'Eternals,' Sets 'Black Panther II' Date|last=Couch|first=Aaron|date=August 24, 2019|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=January 2, 2020}}</ref> ||''[[Black Panther (film)#Sequel|Black Panther II]]''|| \n|-\n| align=\"right\" | {{start date|2022|07|29|}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/indiana-jones-5-release-date-pushed-again-2021-1125975|title=Disney Pushes 'Indiana Jones 5' a Year to 2021, Dates 'Maleficent 2,' 'Jungle Cruise'|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|date=July 10, 2018|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=January 2, 2020}}</ref> || ''[[Indiana Jones (franchise)#Untitled fifth film (2021)|Indiana Jones 5]]'' \n|[[Lucasfilm]]\n|\n|-\n| align=\"right\" | {{start date|2022|07|